%%{init: {"theme": "default"}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Admin as BlazorAdmin<br/>(Browser)
    participant API as PublicApi<br/>(ASP.NET Core)
    participant AppCore as ApplicationCore<br/>(Services)
    participant Infra as Infrastructure<br/>(EfRepository)
    participant DB as SQL Server

    Note over Admin,DB: FLOW-001: Admin Authentication

    Admin->>API: POST api/authenticate {Username, Password}
    API->>Infra: SignInManager.PasswordSignInAsync()
    Infra->>DB: SELECT AspNetUsers WHERE UserName=...
    DB-->>Infra: ApplicationUser
    Infra-->>API: SignInResult.Succeeded
    API->>Infra: IdentityTokenClaimService.GetTokenAsync()
    Note over Infra: ⚠ Uses hardcoded JWT_SECRET_KEY
    Infra->>DB: GetRolesAsync(user)
    DB-->>Infra: ["Administrators"]
    Infra-->>API: JWT token (7-day expiry)
    API-->>Admin: {Token, Username, Result=Succeeded}
    Note over Admin: Sets Bearer header on HttpClient

    Note over Admin,DB: FLOW-002: Admin Lists Catalog Items

    Admin->>Admin: Check localStorage cache (TTL 60s)
    alt Cache miss
        Admin->>API: GET api/catalog-items<br/>GET api/catalog-brands<br/>GET api/catalog-types (parallel)
        API->>Infra: EfRepository<CatalogItem>.ListAsync()
        Infra->>DB: SELECT Catalog, CatalogBrands, CatalogTypes
        DB-->>Infra: Entities
        Infra-->>API: CatalogItem[], CatalogBrand[], CatalogType[]
        API-->>Admin: PagedCatalogItemResponse, ListCatalogBrandsResponse, ...
        Admin->>Admin: Join brand/type names onto items
        Admin->>Admin: Store in localStorage (60s TTL)
    else Cache hit
        Admin->>Admin: Return cached data
    end

    Note over Admin,DB: FLOW-004: Shopper Checkout (Place Order — Web MVC)

    participant Web as Web MVC<br/>(⚠ Source unknown)
    participant Shopper as Shopper

    Shopper->>Web: POST /checkout {basketId, address}
    Web->>AppCore: OrderService.CreateOrderAsync(basketId, address)
    AppCore->>Infra: EfRepository<Basket>.FirstOrDefaultAsync(BasketWithItemsSpec)
    Infra->>DB: SELECT Baskets WHERE Id=... INCLUDE BasketItems
    DB-->>Infra: Basket + Items
    Infra-->>AppCore: Basket
    Note over AppCore: Guard.Against.EmptyBasketOnCheckout
    AppCore->>Infra: EfRepository<CatalogItem>.ListAsync(CatalogItemsSpec)
    Infra->>DB: SELECT Catalog WHERE Id IN (...)
    DB-->>Infra: CatalogItem[]
    Infra-->>AppCore: CatalogItem[] with current prices
    AppCore->>AppCore: Create CatalogItemOrdered snapshots
    AppCore->>AppCore: new Order(buyerId, address, items)
    AppCore->>Infra: EfRepository<Order>.AddAsync(order)
    Infra->>DB: INSERT Orders + OrderItems
    DB-->>Infra: Saved
    Infra-->>AppCore: Order
    AppCore-->>Web: Order created
    Web-->>Shopper: Redirect to order confirmation
    Note over AppCore,DB: ⚠ Basket NOT cleared in OrderService — risk of duplicate checkout
